new all-time high hit by the Big Tech-driven indices, the FOMO gets a little worse. But at the same time, with each new high, the valuation of the market's</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1399327817/image_1399327817.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742520-9-stocks-im-buying-as-the-market-reaches-rare-level-of-speculative-fervor", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 16:05:00"}, {"id": "4742727", "title": "Weekly Indicators: Positive Tone Not Affected By Seasonality Whipsaw", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329036922/image_1329036922.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Unfinished Christmas meal\" data-id=\"1329036922\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329036922/image_1329036922.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329036922/image_1329036922.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329036922/image_1329036922.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329036922/image_1329036922.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329036922/image_1329036922.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329036922/image_1329036922.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329036922/image_1329036922.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329036922/image_1329036922.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">alvarez/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Purpose</h2> <p>I look at the <strong>high frequency weekly indicators</strong> because while they can be very noisy, they provide a good nowcast of the economy, and will telegraph the maintenance or change in the economy well before monthly</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1329036922/image_1329036922.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742727-weekly-indicators-positive-tone-not-affected-by-seasonality-whipsaw", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 16:00:00"}, {"id": "4742813", "title": "EU And Mercosur Seal Agreement Following Decades-Long Negotiations", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/986901672/image_986901672.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"European Union flag\" data-id=\"986901672\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/986901672/image_986901672.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/986901672/image_986901672.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/986901672/image_986901672.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/986901672/image_986901672.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/986901672/image_986901672.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/986901672/image_986901672.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/986901672/image_986901672.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/986901672/image_986901672.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 3